Migrated from EPA STORET Legacy Database- originally reported by Wisconsin DNR
Lake choppy.  Readings done the day after strong winds.
Very windy- 15-21 mph gusts- water stirred up.
Many pan fish and muskys in shallow water.  Observed first water snake of the year.
Sunny- light winds. Had 3" of rain prior day.
Sunny- breezy but light winds at monitoring site
